uently, if we monitor a few multiple quasars, we can find ``echo''-like\nvariation in one of the images after intrinsic flux variations of quasars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Oct 2003 13:58:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
