ition in the standard model. For the\neffective potential this phase transition occurs at the mass range\n$m_{H}\\approx 180$ GeV and for the tree level mass relations at $m_{H}\\approx\n168$ GeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Oct 2003 00:48:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Dec 2003 21:02:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
